othercases @<Complain that \.{\\the} can't do this; give zero result@>
endcases;@/
while cur_val_level>level do @<Convert \(c)|cur_val| to a lower level@>;
@<Fix the reference count, if any, and negate |cur_val| if |negative|@>;
exit:end;

