@ @<Fetch a token list...@>=
if level<>tok_val then
  begin print_err("Missing number, treated as zero");
@.Missing number...@>
  help3("A number should have been here; I inserted `0'.")@/
    ("(If you can't figure out why I needed to see a number,")@/
